results.name: Primes at which difference pattern X4Y (X and Y >= 6) occurs in A001223.
example: 127 is in the sequence because 127 + 4 = 131 is prime, but the difference pattern around 127 is {[113] 14 [127] 4 [131] 6 [137]}.
